expression: text
---
Start HTTP API server

Usage: cdt serve [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>    Output format [default: table] [possible values: json, jsonl, table]
      --project <PROJECT>  Scope to a project (name or encoded ID; use --project=<id> for encoded IDs)
      --json[=<JSON>]      Select JSON fields (comma-separated), implies --format json. Without value: list available fields. Usage: --json=field1,field2
      --no-truncate        Do not truncate fields in table mode
  -h, --help               Print help
